Comment: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,和我很亲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是暗黑骑士？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,暗黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,恶徳之主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,恶魔召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}只会毛毛虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我说佐迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}毛毛虫毛毛虫毛毛虫...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我无论如何都想离开赛琳矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,死吧死吧死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}死吧死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,死掉回到史卡勒海尔大人的怀抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,被抱着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,毛毛虫毛毛虫...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}结果还是毛毛虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,光啊 以卢米埃里斯庇护之名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.75,0:02:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再次确认一下优先顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,第一是我们五人活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是救出蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当然会拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不要勉强乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 梦儿我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,被蓝德说贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿我很受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就算叫他不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他也不会停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就算要让说喜欢这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果梦儿在这种地方孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到蓝德现在的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是因为这种小事就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德早就死过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德等着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,恶德恶德恶德恶德...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}没有这闲工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,只可能是他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那种情况是他一个人爬上来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,至少生命力特别顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他的韧性 是我们没有的资质
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,活下来啊 蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,死吧死吧死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,死吧死吧死吧蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,死吧死吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,贫乳贫乳贫乳贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}要是摸过那对儿贫乳就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,排气法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忽然叫我名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,差点吓死我了 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽姆·爱姆 帕鲁酷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,光啊 以卢米埃里斯庇护的名义下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿这是最后一支箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家来这边 梦儿也来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,能跑么蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,废话 你以为你在跟谁说话啊垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽姆·爱姆 帕鲁酷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,光啊 以卢米埃里斯庇护的名义下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你眼睛湿漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我全身都疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不用这么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易活着重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 我才不想你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到不用再看到你们的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心里就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,心里怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,心疼得要裂开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,心里就？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,心里就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,心 里 就？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:07:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,别叫我贫乳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是要说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说上几百遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,贫乳贫乳贫乳..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上嘴老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说你不用治好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧 回到欧鲁达那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要放松的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等回到欧鲁达那再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我想了一下蓝德对我说的「你是队长」那句话的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到队长就是马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要变得像马纳多那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这种心情 老实说确实有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是谁都是各有长短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多不擅长什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我却根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很多不擅长不会的方面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴们会帮我弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定这就是维持了队伍的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,自己有没有好好履行队长的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,队伍能顺利的走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我和蓝德也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只要战斗能配合好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这才是是最重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:09:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我暂时用不了魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,顶多再用一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,需要找个地方冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太懂魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不过看起来席赫露也快到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,注意不要刺激到低等地精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真难缠！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead spot受伤越重就越强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还要变强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是能逃掉么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的小路肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,至少要留下一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在思考之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,身体就动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在哭么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要死 笨蛋哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,手骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况下叫我不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是魔鬼么 死蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,既然顽强的你都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我自然没有放弃的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,记得来驱散我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话应该还能再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还能再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,关乎性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这是关乎性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,至死都要想办法活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,时间停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在很慢的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咧...梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是...天国？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛 给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead spot呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,接好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,醒了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是赏金30金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等哈尔希洛醒了大家在商量怎么分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他说因为哈尔希洛是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 你有什么意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去接哈尔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,接？啊 那个接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你和date倒在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,DATE？啊 Dead spot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我的剑也断了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个挺趁手的就拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这个趁手...真厉害啊莫古索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,当然这样直接用是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想送去锻造店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看来赏金的用途已经决定好一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,等完成了 必须要取了可爱的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,菜刀君一号之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可...爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 给你修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,身体熟悉的重量和触感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思议的让人觉得平静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,让人忽然觉得有了实感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了 梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在才说？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说了哦 哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,居然干掉了Dead spot真是超厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有点嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,其实没有尼日利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,澳大利亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,莲崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,莲崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多死后那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,莲崎不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是没能够接受马纳多的死而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以谢谢你莲崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们请客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情的喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不能来么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事想问马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你当队长的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有时会觉得很辛苦么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛你很难受么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的自己和今天的自己是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,明天的自己又会变成什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每一天都活在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,去见明天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个世界活得越久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就有记忆变得更加遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说是我们原来世界的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,从什么地方来的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,砰的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,像是忘掉了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我很不安 焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,脚下石阶的触感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吸进去的空气的芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让我感到自己确确实实的在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.99,0:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有不想忘记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也有不能忘记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,无论何时都不会想要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 走吧
